featured_reviews.review_id:
One of the busiest and famous spots in Begusarai.
Well honoured among Muslim community, specifically.
Hundreds of Muslim brothers and sisters throng here and enjoy pious congregation.
Situated at a square, the place is easily traceable.
During afternoon after the Muslims have offered the prayer here, a huge jam is caused here that can last for hours.
Thanks to traffic policemen present at the spot that solve the traffic conundrum created here daily.
